{
    "id": 1,
    "title": "[Unity] 自定义AssetsManager进行资源加载与管理",
    "date": "2025-05-30",
    "author": "Pure_*",
    "content": [
        { "type": "header", "level": 2, "data": "问题的产生" },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "\t1. 游戏通过AssetBundle读取资源，如预制体、图片等",
                "\t2. AssetBundle有很多，并且Bundle之间可能存在依赖，如Bundle A中的预制体使用了Bundle B中的资源",
                "\t3. 同步加载可能造成进程卡死，如资源过大，解压速度慢等"
            ]
        },
        { "type": "header", "level": 2, "data": "思路" },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "\t1. 使用协程进行异步加载",
                "\t2. 加载资源前，先检查Bundle是否被加载，如果没有被加载则先加载Bundle",
                "\t3. 加载Bundle前，先检查是否依赖其他Bundle，如果有有依赖与其他则先加载其他Bundle",
                "\t4. Bundle加载完毕，再加载资源即可"
            ]
        },
        { "type": "header", "level": 2, "data": "本文实现" },
        { "type": "header", "level": 3, "data": "准备工作" },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "1. 首先准备一个记录资源映射的json文件，如下图，key值为资源的路径，value值为资源所在的Bundle名称"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": {
                "url": "../../images/blogs/Blog-AssetsManager-AssetMapping.png",
                "alt": "更新界面截图",
                "caption": "图1 资源与AB的映射表示例"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "2. 建立一个ResConst.cs类，将Bundle中的资源路径填写进去，需要注意的是，此处的路径需要与json文件的key值一致，如下图。"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": {
                "url": "../../images/blogs/Blog-AssetsManager-ResConst.png",
                "alt": "更新界面截图",
                "caption": "图2 ResConst示例"
            }
        },
        { "type": "header", "level": 3, "data": "实现" },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "1. 新建一个AssetsManager.cs作为资源管理器（不一定要叫这个名啊），需要注意的是因为需要使用协程，因此AssetsManager是需要继承自MonoBehavior的，主要有三个字段"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "data": [
                "public class AssetsManager : MonoBehaviour",
                "{",
                "\t// 资源路径 -> Bundle名称",
                "\tprivate Dictionary<string, string> path2bundle = new Dictionary<string, string>();",
                "\t// Bundle名称 -> AssetBundle",
                "\tprivate Dictionary<string, AssetBundle> bundles = new Dictionary<string, AssetBundle>();",
                "\t// 主Bundle的manifest文件",
                "\tprivate AssetBundleManifest mainManifest;",
                "}"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "2. 首先读取主Bundle和它的.manifest，也就是下图这两个文件（在Awake中执行）"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": {
                "url": "../../images/blogs/Blog-AssetsManager-BundleFile.png",
                "alt": "更新界面截图",
                "caption": "图3 导出的AssetBundle示例"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "\t· 主Bundle的名称就为导出Bundle时，导出文件夹的名称（此处就叫Bundle）",
                "\t· 主Bundle的.manifest文件记录了所有Bundle以及其依赖，如下图，红色箭头所指Bundle的名称以及紫色方框中就为其依赖的Bundle",
                "\t· 将主Bundle的manifest文件读取出来，需要注意的是主Bundle的manifest就叫AssetBundleManifest"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "data": [
                "// 初始化主Bundle 方便后续拿依赖",
                "// 主AB包一定存在，而且与导出时的文件夹名相同",
                "DirectoryInfo directory = new DirectoryInfo(GlobalConfig.AssetBundleDir);",
                "string mainPath = Path.Combine(GlobalConfig.AssetBundleDir, directory.Name);",
                "AssetBundle main = AssetBundle.LoadFromFile(mainPath);",
                "// 获取主AB包的配置文件",
                "mainManifest = main.LoadAsset<AssetBundleManifest>(\"AssetBundleManifest\");"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "3. 利用LitJson读取出来并存储到字典中，此处我将资源映射文件AssetMapping.json打到名称为main的Bundle中。（在Awake中执行）"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "data": [
                "// 把资源路径与bundle映射先加载出来",
                "string mappingFile = Path.Combine(GlobalConfig.AssetBundleDir, \"main\");",
                "AssetBundle bundle = AssetBundle.LoadFromFile(mappingFile);",
                "// 加入到Bundle字典中",
                "bundles.Add(\"main\", bundle);",
                "TextAsset mappingText = bundle.LoadAsset<TextAsset>(\"AssetMapping.json\");",
                "JsonReader reader = new JsonReader(mappingText.ToString());",
                "JsonData data = JsonMapper.ToObject(reader);",
                "foreach (string key in data.Keys)",
                "{",
                "\tpath2bundle.Add(key, data[key].ToString());",
                "}",
                "reader.Close();"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "4. 实现加载Bundle。",
                "\t - 先检查依赖",
                "\t - 如果没有依赖了，则代表所有包都已经加载完毕，就返回 ",
                "\t - 否则开启协程加载所有包"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "data": [
                "private void LoadAssetBundle(string bundleName, Action<AssetBundle> onLoaded)",
                "{",
                "\t// 检查出不存在的依赖",
                "\tList<string> deps = CheckNoneExistedDependencies(bundleName);",
                "\t// 如果没有不存在的直接返回",
                "\tif (deps.Count == 0)",
                "\t{",
                "\t\tonLoaded?.Invoke(bundles[bundleName]);",
                "\t}",
                "\telse",
                "\t{",
                "\t// 异步加载",
                "\tList<object> parameters = new List<object>()",
                "\t{",
                "\t\tdeps,",
                "\t\tbundleName,",
                "\t\tonLoaded,",
                "\t};",
                "\tStartCoroutine(nameof(LoadAssetBundlesAsync), parameters);",
                "\t}",
                "}"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "5. 协程LoadAssetBundlesAsync的实现，这一步的关键在于if条件为ture的分支中防止重复加载的yield return语句和false分支中占位的bundles.Add(deps[i], null)语句，主要是基于以下考量",
                "\t - 游戏资源加载是非常频繁的，当同一时间（帧）多个协程加载同一个还未加载的Bundle，如果不控制重复加载，就会报The AssetBundle XXX can't be loaded because another AssetBundle with the same files is already loaded",
                "\t先占位，表明已经有协程在加载这个Bundle了，其他协程到这里只需要等待即可"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "data": [
                "IEnumerator LoadAssetBundlesAsync(List<object> obj)",
                "{",
                "\tList<string> deps = (List<string>)obj[0];",
                "\tstring targetBundleName = (string)obj[1];",
                "\tAction<AssetBundle> onLoaded = (Action<AssetBundle>)obj[2];",
                "\tfor (int i = 0; i < deps.Count; i++)",
                "\t{",
                "\t\tif (bundles.ContainsKey(deps[i]))",
                "\t\t{",
                "\t\t\t// 防止重复加载",
                "\t\t\tyield return new WaitUntil(() => bundles[deps[i]] != null);",
                "\t\t}",
                "\t\telse",
                "\t\t{",
                "\t\t\tstring bundlePath = Path.Combine(GlobalConfig.AssetBundleDir, deps[i]);",
                "\t\t\t// 占位",
                "\t\t\tbundles.Add(deps[i], null);",
                "\t\t\tAssetBundleCreateRequest request = AssetBundle.LoadFromFileAsync(bundlePath);",
                "\t\t\tyield return request;",
                "\t\t\tbundles[deps[i]] = request.assetBundle;",
                "\t\t}   ",
                "\t}",
                "\tonLoaded?.Invoke(bundles[targetBundleName]);",
                "}"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "6. 检查依赖CheckNoneExistedDependencies的实现，函数LoadAssetBundle、协程LoadAssetBundlesAsync和这个函数都是相扣的",
                "\t - 使用主Bundle的manifest，调用GetAllDependencies就能拿到该bundle的所有依赖",
                "\t - 因为存在占位情况，如果此时需要的bundle没有加载出来则需要加入到不存在列表中 ",
                "\t - 最后检查自己存在与否"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "data": [
                "private List<string> CheckNoneExistedDependencies(string bundleName)",
                "{",
                "\tList<string> noneExisted = new List<string>();",
                "\tstring[] dependencies = mainManifest.GetAllDependencies(bundleName);",
                "\tforeach (string dep in dependencies)",
                "\t{",
                "\t\tif (!bundles.ContainsKey(dep) || bundles[dep] == null)",
                "\t\t{",
                "\t\t\tnoneExisted.Add(dep);",
                "\t\t}",
                "\t}",
                "\t// 也要检查自己存不存在",
                "\tif (!bundles.ContainsKey(bundleName) || bundles[bundleName] == null)",
                "\t{",
                "\t\tnoneExisted.Add(bundleName);",
                "\t}",
                "\treturn noneExisted;",
                "}"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "7. 加载资源。当完成上面Bundle的加载，就可以使用ResConst.cs中设定好的路径加载资源了"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "data": [
                "public void LoadAsset(string assetPath, Action<UnityEngine.Object> onLoaded = null)",
                "{",
                "\tif (string.IsNullOrEmpty(assetPath) || string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(assetPath))",
                "\t{",
                "\t\tthrow new ArgumentException(\"Bad Argument: It was NULL , Empty or WhiteSpace\");",
                "\t}",
                "\tif (path2bundle.TryGetValue(assetPath, out string bundleName))",
                "\t{",
                "\t\tLoadAssetBundle(bundleName, (bundle) =>",
                "\t\t{",
                "\t\t\tFileInfo file = new FileInfo(assetPath);",
                "\t\t\tList<object> parameters = new List<object>()",
                "\t\t\t{",
                "\t\t\t\tfile.Name,",
                "\t\t\t\tbundle,",
                "\t\t\t\tonLoaded,",
                "\t\t\t};",
                "\t\t\tStartCoroutine(nameof(LoadAssetAsync), parameters);",
                "\t\t});",
                "\t}",
                "\telse",
                "\t{",
                "\t\tthrow new DirectoryNotFoundException(\"Bad Key: \" + assetPath + \" is not a key of bundle dictionary\");",
                "\t}",
                "}",
                "",
                "// 调用之前保证Bundle都有",
                "IEnumerator LoadAssetAsync(List<object> list)",
                "{",
                "\tstring assetName = (string)list[0];",
                "\tAssetBundle bundle = (AssetBundle)list[1];",
                "\tAction<UnityEngine.Object> onLoaded = (Action<UnityEngine.Object>)list[2];",
                "\tAssetBundleRequest request = bundle.LoadAssetAsync<UnityEngine.Object>(assetName);",
                "\tyield return request;",
                "\tonLoaded?.Invoke(request.asset);",
                "}"
            ]
        }
    ]
}
